resource.title: Treatment plan for ovarian cancer
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including Surgery, Chemotherapy, Radiotherapy

resource.conclusion: Patient shows improving status for ovarian cancer. Aisha Nguyen, a 53-year-old Asian female diagnosed with Stage III ovarian cancer, underwent debulking surgery followed by 6 cycles of chemotherapy and 5 sessions of radiotherapy. She is currently improving post-treatment with regular follow-up care.
